# Backgrounds Folder

Place your background images here.

Suggested images:
- `landing-bg.jpg` - For the main landing page
- `admin-bg.jpg` - For the admin dashboard
- `login-bg.jpg` - For the login page
- `claim-bg.jpg` - For the voucher claim page

Recommended size: 1920x1080 or larger
Recommended format: JPG or WebP for photos, PNG for graphics
